{
  "stem": "1550.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, I remember one-- one incident at one of those islands.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had arrived there, and we got the bread and the water, and then we continued on our way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as we were sailing out, there was this Greek-- [CRYING] there was this Greek priest standing there, on a-- on the edge of the port.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew it was a Greek priest because they have a very specific dress.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he stood there-- [CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Anyway, he raised his hands and he kind of-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he kind of blessed the ship.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] anyway, we continued through these Greek islands, and arrived at-- we arrived at Heraklion in Crete.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We arrived at Heraklion in Crete on October the 16th-- on October 16th.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we ran out of coal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our ship was a coal ship, by the way, and did not have a radio.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I told you, the conditions on the ship were terrible, but I don't have to go through this again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we ran out of coal, and could continue any further.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We did not have enough coal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we were standing there for several weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the meantime, what happened was that the war caught up with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What happened was, on-- on-- I have to check my dates again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "On October-- we arrived in Heraklion on October the 16th.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "On October the 28th, Italy declared war on Greece.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were-- every day, there were air raid alarms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Not air raid attacks, there were air raid alarms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But fortunately there were no air raid attacks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were standing in the-- in the port.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
